  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support athletes with special needs in Pakistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We empower children and youth with varying Intellectual Disabilities (ID) using the power of sports. Our sports camps and dedicated coaches help develop fine motor and sports skills in youth with ID, which enables their participation in life experiences. Our unified sports help build confidence and social skills in athletes. We also deliver coaching clinics for teachers and coaches of special schools to equip them with the expertise to execute our inclusive sports program in a school setting.</narrative>
  </description>
